{"tid":1395881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"口交部：白宮應忠告過激示威者用和平方式表達訴求","createTime":"2019-08-02T01:57:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T02:22:06.000Z","uid":111253,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"9e0baebe1ef851af63d87504d07571dd77b403da","tid":1395881,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T01:57:09.000Z","msg":"美國白宮一名高級官員表示，注意到有關中國解放軍在香港邊境集結的傳聞，又說總統特朗普希望中國在香港問題上，不要有過激的介入。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部發言人華春瑩表示，具體情況不清楚，但她指出，如果白宮真心希望香港和平穩定，應該對過激使用暴力的示威人士提出忠告，要用和平的方式表達訴求，不要用暴力的方式。<br />\n<br />\nSource：<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1471663-20190731.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1471663-20190731.htm&d=oOhF4K9gmG%2F73F8T9h6VFIR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=f50ddb3c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1471663-20190731.htm&h=f0c7e200\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1471663-20190731.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d92e89ba4f9b2b1f91faaf1b51e392b130d5030e","tid":1395881,"uid":51920,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T01:58:02.000Z","msg":"又叫人唔好說三道四 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"305c0d8d80cb27baa244bb814e91ba25989e3559","tid":1395881,"uid":111253,"like":6,"